Checked at the end of
$\mathsf{Exp}^{\mathsf{IND}}$ or
$\mathsf{Exp}^{\mathsf{Privacy}}$.
$\mathsf{WinAuth}$ occurs if some
$\pi^s_i$ accepts yet has no
matching partner $\pi^t_j$,
or two distinct oracles both
accept the same session.
$\mathsf{Adv}^{\mathsf{AUTH}}:=\Pr[\mathsf{WinAuth}]$.
\\
